; Required header — removing or renaming this will break the file.

50:1.5:combos/tier1.ogg:%combo% click combo! Your output is now %multiplier%x per press!
75:2.0:combos/tier2.ogg:%combo% click combo! You're hitting your stride! %multiplier%x per press!
100:2.5:combos/tier3.ogg:%combo% click combo! Incredible baking! %multiplier%x per press!
150:3.0:combos/tier4.ogg:%combo% click combo! Legendary! Your cookies are flying out of the oven at %multiplier%x per press!
